---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'ms';
const post = {
  title: 'Kisah Jaya Penggantian 2026',
  slug: 'kisah-jaya-penggantian-2026',
  excerpt: 'Kisah jaya owner yang ganti peralatan dengan bijak. 0% deposit. Income naik 40%. inspirasi.',
  date: '2026-01-18',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 5,
  category: 'Penggantian & Naik Taraf',
  image: '/images/blog/replacement-success-story-2026.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['kisah jaya penggantian', 'replacement success story malaysia', '0% deposit', 'business upgrade'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/ms' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/ms/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/${lang}/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
      <header class="mb-8">
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Penggantian & Naik Taraf</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
          <span>{post.author}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('ms-MY', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{post.readTime} min baca</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2>Dari Peralatan Lama ke Baru – Income Naik 40%</h2>

        <p>Inilah kisah Encik Razak dari Johor. Beliau ada 2 lori 15 tahun. Selalu rosak, client complain, repair cost makan profit.</p>

        <h2>Masalah Encik Razak</h2>

        <ul>
          <li>2 Lori 15 tahun – selalu breakdown</li>
          <li>Repair cost: RM25K-40K/tahun</li>
          <li>Downtime: 20-30 hari/tahun</li>
          <li>Client complain delay – some pindah ke competitor</li>
          <li>Income stagnan – tak boleh ambil lebih job</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Keputusan: Ganti ke Baru</h2>

        <p>Encik Razak decide untuk ganti kedua-dua lori. Kami bantu dengan:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>0% deposit untuk kedua-dua lori baru</li>
          <li>Trade-in lori lama: RM25K setiap satu</li>
          <li>Financing: RM120K setiap unit</li>
          <li>Installment: RM2,200/lori/bulan</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Results Lepas 6 Bulan</h2>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Downtime:</strong> Dari 25 hari → 3 hari je!</li>
          <li><strong>Repair cost:</strong> Dari RM30K → RM3K/tahun</li>
          <li><strong>Fuel saving:</strong> RM800/lori/bulan</li>
          <li><strong>Client satisfaction:</strong> No more complaints!</li>
          <li><strong>Income:</strong> Naik 40% – boleh ambil lebih job</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Kiraan Bijak</h2>

        <p><strong>Sebelum Ganti:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Income: RM40K/bulan</li>
          <li>Repair: RM2,500/bulan (average)</li>
          <li>Net: RM37,500/bulan</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Sesudah Ganti:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Income: RM56K/bulan (+40%)</li>
          <li>Installment: RM4,400/bulan</li>
          <li>Repair: RM250/bulan (average)</li>
          <li>Net: RM51,350/bulan</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Tambahan Net: RM13,850/bulan!</strong></p>

        <h2>Bank vs Kami</h2>

        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;">
          <thead>
            <tr style="background: #2D1810; color: #D4A574;">
              <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Item</th>
              <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Bank</th>
              <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Kami</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Deposit</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">RM24K-48K</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>RM0</strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background: #F9FAFB;">
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Trade-in</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Nilai rendah</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>Market value</strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Kelulusan</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">3-4 minggu</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>pantas</strong></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
          <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Nak Jaya Macam Encik Razak?</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Ganti peralatan lama anda. 0% deposit untuk unit baru. WhatsApp kami.</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Telefon)</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
        <CTAButton text="Dapatkan Pembiayaan Sekarang" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
      </footer>
    </article>
  </BaseLayout>

  <style>
    h2 { color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    h3 { color: #8B6F47; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    p { line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
    strong { color: #2D1810; font-weight: 700; }
    ul { list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
    li { padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
    li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #D4A574; font-weight: bold; }
  </style>
